{"tid":1846854,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"呢一刻：香港人，團結！","createTime":"2020-01-27T18:20:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T18:48:53.000Z","uid":326930,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"83f0902b4cc0cb29567574416137dda361fc8c5f","tid":1846854,"uid":326930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:20:01.000Z","msg":"無肺去到咁既階段，<br />\n加上港共咁既應對。。。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭條7婆放棄左香港人，而家係到奶到雪雪聲，<br />\n<br />\n無論你係 藍絲廢老 定 黃絲手足，<br />\n<br />\n而家，<br />\n香港人要團結！！！<br />\n<br />\n首先，要防止復工！<br />\n試諗下，大家外出返工，果種交叉感染既爆發力。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1）醫護人員、入境處職員<br />\n你地係最最最前線既人，啲毒下下噴埋來<br />\n唔為自己，都請為下你家人<br />\n<br />\n2）黃藍絲（香港人）<br />\n未來/末日，[未] [末] 只係一劃之差，<br />\n暫時放下過往7個幾月既情緒，<br />\n你要［未來］，請你自發擺工<br />\n你要［末日］，可以自行上班<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">支持醫護入境擺工，請自發擺埋一份！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人，要團結，<br />\n對內，我地可以一家人打生打死<br />\n對外，每個人都係手足，齊心抗敵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟及我全公司同事<br />\n已決定不會於年初八啟市，<br />\n暫時決定擺工至2月17號。<br />\n於2月15號再檢討，視乎當時情況再決定是否繼續。"},{"pid":"cbddc4daeb206c07a5c48758cb57a68155e26dd2","tid":1846854,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">攬炒</span>"},{"pid":"4c6ccb06fdb7fbb002aeaab63e3ca338487b9363","tid":1846854,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:21:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[事關重大請廣傳]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港醫護、海關唔罷工嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護同海關全家在內嘅更多人<br />\n<br />\n大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/edG0Z6X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FedG0Z6X.jpg&h=8ac5b79d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，一齊罷工保護香港，直至港府落實封關"},{"pid":"8a795baf1d98fa3a250e1470db6c1f492b7c2610","tid":1846854,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:21:39.000Z","msg":"4成藍"},{"pid":"3d38dec52d499fc44a2ebac4844b5327feee6351","tid":1846854,"uid":180442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:22:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.29 和你關</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">海關、入境、醫護<br />\n各界人士 一同封關</span></span>"},{"pid":"eb4ef823c7a03624db7ec7602570ed9c89a2046a","tid":1846854,"uid":180442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:22:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.29 和你關</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">海關、入境、醫護<br />\n各界人士 一同封關</span></span>"},{"pid":"39e5e05674151ed4d1237b18495f4716b74dabaa","tid":1846854,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:22:38.000Z","msg":"黎明行動送頭<br />\n港島遊行集會送頭<br />\n深夜整連儂牆送頭<br />\n派傳單都會畀藍絲割肚不了<br />\n<br />\n而家我哋打旗號叫政府封關阻肺炎呀<br />\n民建聯都唔會夠膽出聲反對啦 粉嶺單野政府都hea應啦<br />\n<br />\n另外想問工會過咗咁多個月有幾多人入咗會？<br />\n全民大三罷？<br />\n唔好話無限期啦 就算一日 短期內我都睇唔出我哋有咩條件做得到 到時幾多生化人入咗關？再搞無限期三罷已經遲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因為到時已經有唔少香港人奶咗野 咁醫護仲點罷工呀</span><br />\n<br />\n醒下啦送頭<br />\n你話畀我知唔送頭仲可以點"},{"pid":"8656dcb43d3ba662db2e6f7c3fecac03c5194209","tid":1846854,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:22:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抗疫保命<br />\n推翻政權</span></s